    "description": "Welcome to OWINKA SHOOTER 2.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this hit masterpiece sequel to the hit masterpiece, you return as Owinka 427, two weeks after Sebinka's takeover of the Institute. With the renewed assistance of Jerrbot 2.0 and a hesitant deal with Owinka, it's time to take the Institute back, and earn your freedom!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSebinka is no easy foe, as a new wave of bean shaped Anti-Gamer-Measures are fresh out the oven, ready to stop you at any cost. Sebinka's forces aren't the only issue however, as a new opponent begins to make his way into the fold.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn Owinka Shooter 2, you are reunited with your infinite ammo pistol, alongside some extra firepower as well. With expanded gameplay from the original, Owinka Shooter 2 is sure to keep you engaged through the campaign, also providing plenty of post-story content, such as a revamped Infinite-Wave-A-Tron, and Sandbox.",
